item.title: How to get models out of cache
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

folder options>View
Select show hidden files
De-select hide empty drives
De-select hide extentions
de-select hide protected operating system files.

Go to the models in the cache and click on the first on, while the first one is selected scroll all the way down to the bottom of your folder and while holding down the shift button select the last model. Right click and select properties, there should be a hidden option. De-select that and if the Read-Only option is selected then do the same as with the hidden option.
